name: Shaarlier version 1.3.0
body:
## New Features
- Option to disable certificate validation #7 
- Option to automatically download the description #14 
- Support Basic Access Authentication #16.  A big thanks to @sbarakat !
- Retry notification if share fails

## Bug Fixes
- Download title used to fail on some apps
- The UI is no longer stuck during sharing
- The UI is no longer stuck if the user press _back_ while sharing
- Bug fixes for Android M

## Minor Improvements
- Bug report system is much less aggressive
- If there is no account, the button on the main page says _Add account_ instead of _Manage accounts_ 

## Under the Wood
- Bump to Jsoup 1.8.3
- Bump to Android SDK 23
- Moved most of the network connections to a separate service
